02c98efe4f6d5e8dbd5b7e4","tid":633604,"uid":176197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"公立同私家係一樣，價錢就天同地<br />\n<br />\n無保險堅係唔洗諗私家住，公立做到就繼續<br />\n<br />\n除非有d情況係排到2046， 呢d就點都轉私家，人命嚟架<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/eeltk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feeltk&d=vLOIvQpHADFCD3I8K525qV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6dfc8b81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/eeltk</a>"},{"pid":"7fb98a857f00dbe31b71c876673fbe4f35e7bc2f","tid":633604,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"買保險好多要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0507f7c13390af3da6ea3e19c2a54451905a16","tid":633604,"uid":4037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"祝你爸爸身體健康，大步檻過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e85170981a3e684c5f7cedc927ecf4ee80a0b31","tid":633604,"uid":59671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係本身大腸癌<br />\n做咗手術<br />\n做埋化療<br />\n一直都行得走得好正常<br />\n但2年後轉移咗去肝就急轉直下<br />\n挨多半年就走咗<br />\n根據我老豆嘅經驗<br />\n喺政府到做化療係冇咁舒服<br />\n但政府設備齊全d<br />\n化療期間陪多d老豆啦<br />\n見到佢真係好辛苦<br />\n家人陪伴好重要<br />\n仲有<br />\n我唔記得我老豆嗰陣咩指數唔夠<br />\n有幾次差d落唔到針化療<br />\n要煲花生衣俾佢飲提高個指數<br />\n巴打要撐住<br />\n唔好俾你老豆見到你擔心嗰面<br />\n要一齊樂觀面對"},{"pid":"9d9ef1e0b4b92ae4f8e93ddab5f0cad915943073","tid":633604,"uid":181659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓主<br />\n我爸爸上年9月confirm大腸癌第4期<br />\n之後有做電療化療標靶藥<br />\n去到今年1月remove埋個腫瘤出黎<br />\n依加癌指數已經跌左好多 叫做去番穩定水平<br />\n依加仲可以去到番下工<br />\n多d陪住佢支持住佢<br />\n如果打標靶經濟困難可以揾防癌會申請資助架<br />\n努力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4754f298e4a7a69daf15864b1b251