家<br />\n但公立唔比私人差 <br />\n定期要照全身ct去私家會快過公立<br />\n<br />\n做化療會影響胃口 依家最好盡量儲肥佢<br />\n要買定化療奶粉 要食多d牛肉<br />\n做化療會令到白血球低<br />\nGoogle 搵 星希亞 佢有教食咩維他命補充身體<br />\n屋企人做完化療都有keep 住食<br />\n唔好壓力咁大 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<br />\n希望家父可以食多d 野<br />\n因為一食野就會肚脹<br />\n請問仲布冇rq營養餐單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T00:30:53.000Z","msg":"煲湯 飲湯會肥<br />\n煲湯唔好落中藥<br />\n少量多餐"},{"pid":"b2068de7340ee329b4918035460ac409c872794f","tid":633604,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6f18f38dc1d250fb21019e7a33622b0379b7f5f","tid":633604,"uid":3921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0d697cbcb873bae90165669b4f0709e500ebd10","tid":633604,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:18:49.000Z","msg":"第3期就咪晒錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去公立啦<br />\nbtw, 你老豆平時飲食點？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:54:25.000Z","msg":"飲酒，冇食飯，冇食菜<br />\n請大家警惕自己既飲食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"冇食飯？"},{"pid":"40c12658bd40b7e583fc333388ac5ac99c21b068","tid":633604,"uid":100368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"cda8ef366ad9bcb1675060194dc20d09a3fec02a","tid":633604,"uid":72346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ee5d8c64c8591934d53d54ea95dc49d9c0f34c4","tid":633604,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"希望巴打屋企人冇事"},{"pid":"271ef8f6dba178e49adefd639b1309e8967f9c3e","tid":633604,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"佢有咩病徵發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05a1b4b59067eb4d5dd7c86fbce307595379e40","tid":63